you're talking about.

57:51.780 --> 57:52.648
Hey.

57:53.515 --> 57:54.416
Look at me.

57:57.019 --> 57:59.388
Don't make me shoot you, huh.

58:02.090 --> 58:02.957
Bam, bam.

58:07.029 --> 58:10.699
I'm gonna puke.

58:34.556 --> 58:35.991
Emily, look at me.

58:38.093 --> 58:40.996
Jesus, let's get this
thing going for fuck's sake.

58:44.399 --> 58:45.501
Don't listen to him.

58:47.135 --> 58:49.137
I know you're scared but
we're not gonna hurt you.

58:50.172 --> 58:51.740
I need you to answer
me two things,

58:53.742 --> 58:55.110
did you talk to the fed?

59:01.783 --> 59:03.252
Is Danny dead?

59:04.286 --> 59:05.220
Did you kill him?

59:13.595 --> 59:14.496
Danny's not dead.

59:14.530 --> 59:15.764
We hid him from the feds.

59:19.268 --> 59:20.402
They weren't gonna help him,

59:20.435 --> 59:21.637
and they're not
gonna help Motley,

59:21.670 --> 59:23.539
they're just using
him for something.

59:27.142 --> 59:28.343
He's staying with Mot.

59:29.778 --> 59:31.747
He's meeting him, he's with him.

59:35.517 --> 59:36.518
Do you know where?

59:43.759 --> 59:46.395
He said, "He's staying
here until he gets Danny."

59:54.303 --> 59:56.238
Tell Danny, I'm sorry
I talked to them.

59:58.774 --> 1:00:00.108
What?

1:00:00.142 --> 1:00:01.710
She told us everything
we needed to know.

1:00:03.412 --> 1:00:04.680
She was with the fed earlier,

1:00:04.713 --> 1:00:06.515
