for more information,

1:00:06.548 --> 1:00:08.283
you sloppy son of a bitch.

1:00:09.484 --> 1:00:12.220
Yeah, yeah, yeah,
that little fuck,

1:00:12.254 --> 1:00:13.622
he's with the fed right now.

1:00:15.157 --> 1:00:17.292
Besides the boss says,
"To clean it all up."

1:00:21.730 --> 1:00:24.333
You know you perplex me, Boon,

1:00:25.667 --> 1:00:29.237
last week you and me were
sinking a body in the river,

1:00:32.407 --> 1:00:35.410
and today looks like
you're questioning

1:00:35.444 --> 1:00:36.812
your whole fucking life.

1:00:55.397 --> 1:00:56.365
Yeah.

