1:02:32.028 --> 1:02:33.695
I ain't never killed a fed, you?

1:02:38.467 --> 1:02:39.768
Put that thing out.

1:02:41.970 --> 1:02:43.538
With all due respect

1:02:43.572 --> 1:02:45.941
I'm gonna smoke this
