1:02:45.974 --> 1:02:47.275
and if you don't like it

1:02:47.309 --> 1:02:48.443
then we can squabble it out

1:02:48.477 --> 1:02:50.046
when all this is
done and over with.

1:02:50.079 --> 1:02:50.946
Is that okay?

1:02:52.848 --> 1:02:54.516
I don't like
you being nervous.

1:02:56.986 --> 1:02:59.387
And I'm not fuckin'
nervous, all right.

1:02:59.421 --> 1:03:00.255
I'm not.

1:03:03.525 --> 1:03:04.559
Just excited is all.

1:03:07.763 --> 1:03:08.630
Let's go.

1:03:20.442 --> 1:03:21.576
What you got there?

1:03:23.345 --> 1:03:25.947
It's uh, my father's ashes.

1:03:27.849 --> 1:03:28.717
Really?

1:03:30.685 --> 1:03:32.521
You uh, think I'll
be able to keep 'em,

1:03:32.554 --> 1:03:35.824
you know if me and my mom
get in witness protection?

1:03:35.857 --> 1:03:37.026
Yeah, yeah, of course.

1:03:37.059 --> 1:03:39.694
Yeah, this is Agent Tanner.

1:03:39.728 --> 1:03:41.830
Yeah, can you put me
through to Lloyd please?

1:03:43.398 --> 1:03:44.566
No, no, no, that's okay.

1:03:44.599 --> 1:03:49.005
Um, just tell him to call me
back at uh, 555-8320, room 114.

1:03:57.379 --> 1:03:58.747
